(58, 156, 'Prachtige watermeloen', 'prachtige-watermeloen', '', '<p>Watermeloen is een prachtige en gezonde tractatie. Wij kweken de zoetste watermeloen van de wereld. Wij hebben de grootste watermeloenvelden van ons land.</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 30, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Fruitwinkel webmaster', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(59, 157, 'Wrapper Module', 'wrapper-module', '', '<p>Deze module toont een iFrame venster op een aangegeven locatie. <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Wrapper" title="Wrapper Module">Help</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule wrapper,Wrapper}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 67, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-17 22:35:00', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 8, 0, 1, '', '', 1, 15, '', 0, '*', ''),
(60, 158, 'Nieuwsfeeds', 'nieuwsfeeds', '', '<p>Nieuwsfeeds (com_newsfeeds) biedt een manier voor het organiseren en presenteren van nieuwsfeeds. Nieuwsfeeds is een manier om informatie van een andere website op uw eigen website te presenteren. Bijvoorbeeld de  joomla.org website heeft talrijke feeds die u kunt integreren in uw website. U kunt een menu gebruiken om een enkele feed te presenteren, een lijst van feeds in een categorie of een lijst van alle feedcategorie&euml;n. <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Components_Newsfeeds_Feeds">Help</a></p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 21, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-01-10 04:17:08', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 2, 0, 4, '', '', 1, 2, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(61, 159, 'Kruimelpad Module', 'kruimelpad-module', '', '<p>Kruimelpaden bieden een pad voor gebruikers om te navigeren door uw website. <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;keyref=Help16:Extensions_Module_Manager_Breadcrumbs" title="Kruimelpad Module">Help</a></p>\r\n<div class="sample-module">{loadmodule breadcrumbs,breadcrumbs}</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 75, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-17 22:10:19', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":""}', 5, 0, 2, '', '', 1, 8, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(62, 160, 'Inhoud', 'inhoud-plugins', '', '<p>Inhoudplugins worden actief als specifieke pagina''s worden geladen. Ze doen dingen als e-mailadressen beschermen tegen e-mailharvesters en aanmaken paginascheidingen.</p>\r\n<p>Standaard aan:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Email verbergen <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Email_Cloaking">Help</a></li>\r\n<li>Laad Module <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Load_Modules">Help</a></li>\r\n<li>Paginascheiding <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Pagebreak">Help</a></li>\r\n<li>Paginanavigatie<a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Page_Navigation"> Help</a></li>\r\n<li>Stemmen <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Vote">Help</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Standaard uit:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Code markeren (GeSHi) <a href="http://help.joomla.org/proxy/index.php?option=com_help&amp;amp;keyref=Help17:Extensions_Plugin_Manager_Edit#Content_-_Code_Highlighter_.28GeSHi.29">Help</a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 1, 0, 0, 25, '2011-01-01 00:00:01', 42, 'Joomla!', '2011-09-06 06:11:50', 42, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-01-01 00:00:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_readmore":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_hits":"","page_title":"","alternative_readmore":"","layout":""}', 2, 0, 7, '', '', 1, 1, '', 0, '*', ''),
